      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>title: Java Web学习之JSP（三）<br>comments: true<br>categories: “Java Web”<br>tags:</p><pre><code>- JSP</code></pre><h2 id="一、什么是JSP"><a href="#一、什么是JSP" class="headerlink" title="一、什么是JSP"></a>一、什么是JSP</h2><p>1）JSP 是简 Servlet 编写的一种技术, 它将 Java 代码和 HTML 语句混合在同一个文件中编写,只对网页中的要动态产生的内容采用 Java 代码来编写，而对固定不变的静态内容采用普通静态 HTML 页面的方式编写。 </p><p>2） Java Server Page: Java 服务器端网页. 在 HTML 页面中编写 Java 代码的页面。</p><p>简单的程序：</p><p>​    新建一个JSP页面，在body节点内的&lt;% %&gt;内即可编写Javadiamante。</p><p>​    编写jsp文件内Java代码时，需要导包。</p><p>​    下面第一行代码需要写到.jsp文件第一行，类似于Java导包。</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%@ page <span class="keyword">import</span>=<span class="string">"java.util.Date"</span>%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">Date data = <span class="keyword">new</span> Date();</span><br><span class="line">System.out.print(date);</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/body&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3）JSP 可以放置在 WEB 应用程序中的除了 WEB-INF 及其子目录外的其他任何目录中，JSP 页面的访问路径与普通 HTML 页面的访问路径形式也完全一样。</p><p>4）JSP的运行原理: JSP 本质上是一个 Servlet。</p><p>每个JSP 页面在第一次被访问时， JSP 引擎将它翻译成一个 Servlet 源程序，接着再把这个 Servlet 源程序编译成 Servlet 的 class 类文件。</p><p>然后再由WEB容器（Servlet引擎）像调用普通Servlet程序一样的方式来装载和解释执行这个由JSP页面翻译成的Servlet程序。</p><h2 id="二、JSP页面的9个隐含对象"><a href="#二、JSP页面的9个隐含对象" class="headerlink" title="二、JSP页面的9个隐含对象"></a>二、JSP页面的9个隐含对象</h2><p><strong>def：没有声明就可以使用的对象， JSP页面一共有 9 个隐含对象。</strong></p><p>查看JSP编译后生成的Java文件（Java文件详情请看”Javaweb问题“标签）</p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">_jspService</span><span class="params">(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">throws</span> java.io.IOException, ServletException </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">PageContext pageContext = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">HttpSession session = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ServletContext application = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ServletConfig config = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">JspWriter out = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">Object page = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//使用  &lt;% %&gt; 编写的代码在此位置. 可以用到 request, response, pageContext, session</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//application, config, out, page 这 8 个隐含对象。</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//(实际上还可以使用一个叫 exception 的隐含对象)</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//共九个隐含对象，可不用导包直接在JSP脚本片段中直接引用。</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>①request：HttpServletRequest的一个对象</strong></p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">String name = request.getParameter()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>②response：HttpServletResponse的一个对象（在JSP页面中几乎不会调用response的任何方法）</p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.printl(response <span class="keyword">instanceof</span> HttpServletResponse);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>③pageContext：页面的上下文，是PageContext的一个对象，可以从该对象中获取到其他8个隐含对象，也可以从中获取到当前页面的其他信息。（学习自定义标签时使用它）</strong></p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ServletRequest rep = pageContext.getRequest();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>④session：代表浏览器和副武器的一次回话，是HttpSession的一个对象。</strong></p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.printlin(session.getId());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>⑤application：代表当前Web应用，是ServletContext对象</strong></p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(application.getInitParameter(<span class="string">"password"</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>⑥config：当前JSP对应的Servlet的ServletConfig对象（几乎不用），若需要访问当前JSP配置的初始化参数，需要通过映射的地址才可以访问。</p><p>映射JSP：</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;servlet&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;servlet-name&gt;hellojsp&lt;/servlet-name&gt;    //需要与下面&lt;servlet-name&gt;相同</span><br><span class="line">&lt;jsp-file&gt;/hello.jsp&lt;/jsp-file&gt;          //跳转页面</span><br><span class="line">&lt;init-param&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;param-name&gt;test&lt;/param-name&gt;       //初始化参数</span><br><span class="line">&lt;param-value&gt;testValue&lt;/param-value&gt;//初始化参数值</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/init-param&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/servlet&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;servlet-mapping&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;servlet-name&gt;hellojsp&lt;/servlet-name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;url-pattern&gt;/hellojsp&lt;/url-pattern&gt;  //跳转页面名字</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(config.getInitParameter(<span class="string">"test"</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>⑦out：是JspWriter的对象，调用out.println()可以直接将字符串打印到浏览器。</strong></p><p>⑧page：指向当前JSP对应的Servlet对象的引用，到位Object类型，只能调用Object类的方法（几乎不使用）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">out.println(request.getParameter(&quot;name&quot;));</span><br><span class="line">out.println(&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>⑨exception：在声名了page指令的isErrorPage=“true”时，才可以使用。</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%@ page isErrorPage=&quot;true&quot; %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对属性的作用域的范围从小到大：pageContext，request，session，application</p><h2 id="三、JSP语法"><a href="#三、JSP语法" class="headerlink" title="三、JSP语法"></a>三、JSP语法</h2><p><strong>1、JSP编码的设定</strong></p><p>1）JSP模板元素：JSP页面中的静态HTML内容。</p><p>2)JSP表达式（expression）提供了蒋一个Java变量或表达式的计算结果输出到客户端简化方式，它将要输出的变量或表达式直接封装在&lt;%= 和 %&gt;之间。</p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">String ageStr = request.getParameter(<span class="string">"age"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">Integer age = Integer.parseInt(ageStr);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(age &gt;=<span class="number">18</span> )&#123;</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">成人...</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        未成人...</span><br><span class="line">&lt;%</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3)JSP声名：JSP声名将Java代码封装在&lt;%! 和 %&gt;之中，它里面的代码将被插入进Servlet的_jspServlet方法的外面。（在JSP注释可以组织Java代码的执行）</p><p>4）JSP注释的格式：&lt;%– JSP 注释 –%&gt;<!-- HTML 注释 --></p><p>区别：JSP注释可以阻止Java代码的执行。</p><h2 id="四、域对象的属性操作"><a href="#四、域对象的属性操作" class="headerlink" title="四、域对象的属性操作"></a>四、域对象的属性操作</h2><p>1）方法</p><p>void setAttribute(String name, Object o): 设置属性 。</p><p>Object getAttribute(String name): 获取指定的属性。</p><p>Enumeration getAttributeNames(): 获取所有的属性的名字组成的 Enumeration 对象。</p><p>removeAttribute(String name): 移除指定的属性。</p><p>2）域对象</p><p>pageContext，request，sission，application对象都是上述方法，这四个对象称之为域对象。</p><p>pageContext：属性的作用范围仅限于当前JSP页面</p><p>request：属性的作用范围仅限于同意请求。</p><p>session：属性的作用范围仅限于一次回话：浏览器打开知道关闭称之为一次回话（在此期间，会话不失效）。</p><p>application：属性的作用范围限于当前Web应用，食饭未最大的属性作用范围，只要在一处设置属性，在其他各处的JSP或Servlet中都可以获得。</p><p>jsp文件</p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;% </span><br><span class="line">pageContext.setAttribute(<span class="string">"pageContextAttr"</span>, <span class="string">"pageContextValue"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">request.setAttribute(<span class="string">"requestAttr"</span>, <span class="string">"requestValue"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">session.setAttribute(<span class="string">"sessionAttr"</span>, <span class="string">"sessionValue"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">application.setAttribute(<span class="string">"applicationAttr"</span>, <span class="string">"applicationValue"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">pageContextAttr: &lt;%= pageContext.getAttribute(<span class="string">"pageContextAttr"</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">requestAttr: &lt;%= request.getAttribute(<span class="string">"requestAttr"</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">sessionAttr: &lt;%= session.getAttribute(<span class="string">"sessionAttr"</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">applicationAttr: &lt;%= application.getAttribute(<span class="string">"applicationAttr"</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href="attr_2.jsp"&gt;To Attr2 Page&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href="testAttr"&gt;To Attr Servlet&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;% </span><br><span class="line">request.getRequestDispatcher(<span class="string">"/attr_2.jsp"</span>).forward(request, response);</span><br><span class="line">%&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>servlet文件</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PrintWriter out = response.getWriter();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//1. 在 Servlet 中无法得到 pageContext 对象</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//2. request</span></span><br><span class="line">Object requestAttr = request.getAttribute(<span class="string">"requestAttr"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"requestAttr: "</span> + requestAttr);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//3. session</span></span><br><span class="line">Object sessionAttr = request.getSession().getAttribute(<span class="string">"sessionAttr"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"sessionAttr: "</span> + sessionAttr);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//4. application</span></span><br><span class="line">Object applicationAttr = getServletContext().getAttribute(<span class="string">"applicationAttr"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"applicationAttr: "</span> + applicationAttr);</span><br><span class="line">out.print(<span class="string">"&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
